text: Ilansky (masculine), Ilanskaya (feminine), or Ilanskoye (neuter) may refer to: *Ilansky District, a district of Krasnoyarsk Krai, Russia *Ilansky Urban Settlement, a municipal formation which the district town of Ilansky in Krasnoyarsk Krai, Russia is incorporated as *Ilansky (town), a town in Krasnoyarsk Krai, Russia *Ilanskaya, former name of the town of Ilansky in Krasnoyarsk Krai, Russia
title: Ilansky
